steps.title: I expand the Structure Search panel on 'Advanced search' Page
I open the Structure Editor via the Structure Search pane on the Advanced Search page
I set a Structure Query "benzene" into the Structure Editor in Advanced search page
I click "Transfer" button in the Structure Search Editor in Advanced search page
I click on button 'Search' on page 'Advanced Search'
'Search Results' page is opened
I click on link 'Transfer to Search' on 1st row of page 'Results' after Structure Search
I click on 'Search' button on 'Structure search'  under New Home Page
'Structure search' message should display "results found for Structure Query" above the Search Results grid on the Search Results page

testcase.title: 002) A scenario to check Issue with Elemental structure editor from Structure Search

steps.title: the page "Home" should be loaded on log on
I click on 'Structure search' link on New Home page
I open the Structure Editor via the Structure Search pane on the new Home page
I upload mol file with name "quazolast.mol" on new Structure Search
I click "Transfer" button in the Structure Search Editor on new Header
I click on 'Search' button on 'Structure search'  under New Home Page
'Structure search' message should display "results found for Structure Query" above the Search Results grid on the Search Results page
I click on button 'Back' on browser
